貿易的推進表示，「日本是美國的同盟國，而且也重視與中國的關係。希望日本發揮更大的作用」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:52:35.000Z","msg":"長期合作比中國占盡便宜，仲要呢個係日日發表地球第一恐嚇世界既獨裁國家黎，今日醒悟想真正公平合作，但係匪國就根本唔想公平，只想繼續偷、呃、搶，而你呢d舔共小國新加坡，走出黎吠兩聲又走番去共匪腳邊舔腳指？吠得咁過癮？"},{"pid":"5aef9f1686a2cb480c62cde5117c20d23d2ccda6","tid":1189813,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e74723ecb9870aa2f62023f270380a58b6f8f08a","tid":1189813,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:54:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>李<strong>顯</strong>龍都係咁講<br />\n<br />\n新加坡總理: 阻止中國發展並非明智之舉<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1181471/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1181471/page/1</a></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"仲有外交部長<br />\n<br />\n新加坡力勸美國接受中國崛起 勿傷害其他國家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1157093\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1157093</a>"},{"pid":"9ed48e667b8d69355bc53ebb896dbf6bf66635ca","tid":1189813,"uid":10757,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"美中對撞新加坡受重傷 4月電子產品出口暴跌16.3％<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cmmedia.com.tw/home/articles/15904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmmedia.com.tw%2Fhome%2Farticles%2F15904&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=eb53a5b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cmmedia.com.tw/home/articles/15904</a><br />\n<br />\n唉 嬲嬲豬喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fb413744299e62b5ba4eb20703525e27847057","tid":1189813,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aef9f1686a2cb480c62cde5117c20d23d2ccda6","tid":1189813,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e74723ecb9870aa2f62023f270380a58b6f8f08a","tid":1189813,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime